product.title: Easy Planking Thermo-Treated 1/2 in. x 16 in. x 16 in. Barn Wood Wall Decorative Panel / Picture Frame (4 Sq. Ft. per 2-Pack)
product.description: Wall art panels are made with a new generation of wood material, which reproduces a 350-year old structure of wood on a molecular level. We use our patented thermo-treatment technology to speed up the aging of the wood. If you compare the cell structure of 350-year old wood with the thermo-treated wood (see in the picture), you'll see that they are similar. So, we make a real 350-year old wood with our process, but it is a new product! Easy Planking wall art panels add character, warmth, and a rustic feel to any residential or commercial wall decor. In opposite to reclaimed lumber, which was staying outdoors for decades, our product is free of any insects and bacteria. Change the look of any room by adding the natural beauty of wood to your home or office decor. Easy Planking wall art panels are a real old-wood product, which creates a unique design solution for reclaimed lumber as wall decals or old-wood fashion interior styles. Use our wall art panels as a wall accent, picture frames, a substrate for collections of pictures, musical discs, photos, or any objects. Due to thermo-treatment of wood, use Easy Planking wall art panels even in bathrooms and in other high humidity areas.
feature_bullets: Meets highest grading standards for strength and appearance
Easy to cut, fasten and paint, perfect for many building projects
Durable for your deck and outdoor projects
descriptive_attributes: The Easy Planking wall art panels have a deep 3D wood structure as they are wire brushed
As we use natural wood, each panel will have a slightly different color, shade and structure, which provide you with a decor that is truly a unique piece of art
The product is made from American hardwood in the USA
Thermo-treatment makes wood dimensionally stable and durable
The wood has a walnut-like brown color throughout wood and treated with different colors and designs
Thermo-treatment gives the wood a Class B Fire Rated (better than non-treated wood, which is rated as a Class C)
Our wood wall art panels are 100% natural and Green - no chemicals used
Each wall art panel is approx. 16 in. x 16 in. with an approximate weight of 2 lbs. Two panels in a pack
The backing horizontal planks allow hanging up the wall art panels on one or two nails in the wall as an artwork
Versus pressure-treated softwood: WellDone is 100% green product, doesn't crack, shrink and swell as pressure-treated lumber
Versus composite: WellDone is not overheating under sunlight and it is a real wood
Versus exotic woods: WellDone is much lighter in weight, easier to work with, more stable in sizes and better in appearance
WellDone oak decks are priced at the same level as composite decks, cheaper than exotic, and more expensive than pressure-treated pine decks
WellDone oak is a natural wood and can be installed in the same way as any wood deck (screws, clips), oiling is strongly recommended - see installation instruction for details
2 Pack board square footage - 4.0 sq. ft.
Janka hardness - 1,300 lb.; weight - 3.0 lb./sq. ft.
